applyWebEntityCreationRule

protected WebEntity applyWebEntityCreationRule(WebEntityCreationRule rule,
                                               PageItem page)
Applies web entity creation rule to a page. If the rule is the default rule, or if the page lru matches the rule lruprefix, a match is attempted between page lru and rule regular expression. If there is a match, a web entity is created.

Parameters:
rule - web entity creation rule
page - page
Returns:
created web entity or null
